snippet.title: Demon Blue (Dos game 1992)
snippet.description:
02:04 game play

Demon Blue is a VGA graphics game that you should collect all keys.
It's made by MicroValue, Hirographics.
And it's released for other platforms (Amiga, Commodore 64).

By the way, this game is so difficult.
